OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSri Lanka's tea farmers    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstruggling to survive      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Leaves from the lush green tea estates 
OL,6, covering the hills of central Sri Lanka
OL,7, end up in cups across the world.       
OL,9,FTea is the island's biggest export,    
OL,10,Fnormally bringing in more than $1bn a  
OL,11,Fyear, but the industry is being hard   
OL,12,Fhit by the unprecedented economic      
OL,13,Fcrisis.                                
OL,15,FMost of Sri Lanka's tea is grown by    
OL,16,Fsmaller farmers, like Rohan Tilak      
OL,17,FGurusinghe, who owns two acres of land 
OL,18,Fclose to the village of Kadugunnawa.   
